  "title": "A bright red and green UFO spotted in Taquara-RS [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/a-bright-red-and-green-ufo-spotted-in-taquara-rs-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1aH",
  "content": "<p class=\"p1\" style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 21st, 1996</strong>. Time: 01h30 am. Duration: 90 minutes. In the region of Taquara, State of Rio Grande do Sul, three people spotted an unidentified flying object in the shape of a bright star, in red and green colors. According to the witnesses&#8217; report, the UFO flew at &#8220;very slow&#8221; speed, following a straight path, when it was observed &#8220;in the opposite direction from the East&#8221;, that is, in the West direction. The witnesses saw the UFO with the naked eye and in a clear sky, and they were unable to estimate the altitude of the unknown object.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.422. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Taquara, Estado do Rio Grande do Sul”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>MARCH 21st, 1996. Time: 01h30 am. Duration: 90 minutes. In the region of Taquara, State of Rio Grande do Sul, three people spotted an unidentified flying object in the shape of a bright star, in red and green colors. According to the witnesses&#8217; report, the UFO flew at &#8220;very slow&#8221; speed, following a straight path, [&hellip;]</p>\n",
